University Library


Collections


Maps and Geographic Information Systems






Maps and Geographic Information Systems
Maps & GIS collections are located at the Richard J. Daley Library in Chicago.
These collections include more than 179,000 maps, 2,000 atlases, 150,000 aerial photographs, a small collection of map-related reference books and digital data.





